{%- set object_context = object ?? {} -%}
{%- set object_layout = object_context.layout ?? ('list-' ~ layout) -%}

<div id="wrap" class="col-lg-8 col-md-8">

<h1>coreBOS Configuration Options Store</h1>

<p>Here you can find a whole set of different configuration options which can be used in your application directly or with easy modifications to adapt them to your needs. You can find Business Mappings, Business Actions, Menus, Workflows, change sets and explanations on how to use them to make your coreBOS install even more awesome than it already is!!</p>

<div class="notices blue">Please share your congiurations with us to enrich this library!</div>

<div id="flex-objects">
  <div class="text-center">
    <input class="form-input search" type="text" placeholder="Search by name, description, etc" />
    <button class="button button-primary sort asc" data-sort="name">
      Sort by Name
    </button>
  </div>

  <ul class="list">
    {% for object in collection.filterBy({ published: true }) %}
      <li>
        {% render object layout: object_layout with object_context %}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
</div>

<script>
    var options = {
        valueNames: [ 'name', 'configtype', 'configsubtype', 'description', 'author', 'entry-extra' ]
    };
    var flexList = new List('flex-objects', options);
</script>